      "content": "i see. can you expand on why you think the demographic makeup in Sector B is a factor in the need for more patrols? when you say the demographic indicates a need for more presence to \"maintain order,\" are you implying that the higher concentration of Black residents inherently increases the risk of social friction or crime compared to Sector A?",
